<sec>
<st>
Awards</st>
<p>

Lorenzo's Oil was nominated twice at the <award wordnetid="106696483" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../279/2319279.xml">
65th Academy Awards</link></award>
